### Authentication Endpoints

# Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

###

# Signup - Student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@student.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "role": "student"
}

